" Cheat Sheet
" ===========
" <A> Alt
" <S> Shift
" <C> Control
" <D> Command (or apple key on Macs)
" <M> Meta (Windows key)
"
" <CR> Carriage Return (Enter)
" <C-O> switch to normal mode for the following alias command
" <left>, <right>, <up>, <down> arrow keys

" GENERAL SETUP
" -------------
set nocompatible
syntax enable
set encoding=utf-8
filetype plugin indent on

call pathogen#infect()
